{"tid":793144,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"香港電腦商會創會會長張耀成:「其實而家仲買砌機、底板，都已經過時啦！」","createTime":"2018-08-25T06:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T16:59:08.000Z","uid":58335,"like":2,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"56f8e81723344552e4b8b0783ec10994232df2ce","tid":793144,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T06:55:20.000Z","msg":"on9,同一個餡你睇下砌機平,定買電莖機??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係呃下C9就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「香港電腦通訊節2018」（下稱電腦節）將於本周五至下周一在灣仔會議展覽中心一號展覽廳舉行，參展商數目超過200個，佔地逾600個展位，張耀成表示，會場內將有三分之一的攤位售賣電競產品，較去年多三成，單單出售電競椅的攤檔已有10間，較去年多出數倍。<br />\n<br />\n張指出，近年花得起錢的消費者大有人在，他們均要求品質、技術，非以金錢為主要考慮：「好似電話咁，iphoneX咁貴都咁多人買，其實有好多牌子平好多！就係因為要牌子、質素，唔需要平價。」故他指電腦展轉型實為必要。<br />\n<br />\n他又提到，近年港府開始力推電競產業，加上外界的認受性影響，不少家長對「電競」改觀。他指出，以滑鼠為例，普通用作文書的款式，售價可能不足100元，但電競要求「夠快、夠爽」這類型的滑鼠，則需達500元至600元。<br />\n<br />\n另外，去年電腦節已增加較多的電競主打產品出售，即使是全場最貴產品的ASUS電競水冷枱，拍賣價近7萬多元仍能覓到知音，為張耀成的轉營大計打下強心針。<br />\n問到深水埗的「腦場電腦節」舉行時間接近，會否擔心客源被分散。張耀成說，兩個展覽一向「各有各做」，故未有擔心：「<span style=\"color: red;\">我哋今年係以最潮貨品，望殺出一條血路，宜家啲人賣嘢係睇有無價值，其實而家仲買砌機、底板，都已經過時啦！</span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加上旅發局合作電競音樂節同場舉行，一班平日較少外出的年輕人將有機會前來觀賽，所以期望入場人數較去年上升一成，超過80萬人次。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/225518/%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E7%AF%802018-7%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%B5%E6%B0%B4%E5%86%B7%E6%9E%B1%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%B7-%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E8%BD%89%E5%9E%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E9%AC%A5%E5%B9%B3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F225518%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E7%25AF%25802018-7%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%2586%25B7%25E6%259E%25B1%25E9%2583%25BD%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B2%25B7-%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25BD%2589%25E5%259E%258B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2586%258D%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E5%25B9%25B3&d=5x1QOSNoo%2Fcqy4xx7jWshZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=c04f876f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/225518/%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E7%AF%802018-7%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%B5%E6%B0%B4%E5%86%B7%E6%9E%B1%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%B7-%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E8%BD%89%E5%9E%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E9%AC%A5%E5%B9%B3</a>"},{"pid":"f6a56db31dbf73675da610d5118c1f41e1c269ce","tid":793144,"uid":140454,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T06:58:42.000Z","msg":"如果只係貴少少包埋保養同上門維修我又唔介意<br />\n問題係好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b59055eb5f02526d00145fd6ffd41c977f0e98","tid":793144,"uid":124584,"like":71,"dislike":3,"score":68,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T07:02:46.000Z","msg":"九唔搭八 砌機啲料同廠機有咩分別"},{"pid":"75e1f9337950b752bd7a0a5d67ffe4e1a4f1b8cb","tid":793144,"uid":32577,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T07:05:24.000Z","msg":"同李嘉誠話用1000蚊紙冇用冇分別"},{"pid":"c34e1f0d1cc890fef8bf2a86f4bb932468467ffa","tid":793144,"uid":88719,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T07:08:12.000Z","msg":"張電莖枱咪又係砌機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7679c6db8c7e50b77d6a4cae670e8610cbb5ed","tid":793144,"uid":13151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT